metaResult.collection.name: TensorBox
metaResult.description: Inspired by the abstract art movement, this project is an experimentation of color, texture and light on an artistic composition of a basic form. Resembling Piet Mondrian’s artwork, this collection uses rectangles as the basic form, adding a third dimension and innovative placement of rectangles to create a 3D canvas. The color, texture and light of these rectangles are then assigned through a parametric approach. The result is a collection of 1000 TensorBoxes with unique composition and some mesmerizing compositions.
